OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine start with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, though becoming breezier and
OL,7,Fcloudier through the day. Staying dry,
OL,8,Fwith the best of the brighter spells
OL,9,Fin the south. Feeling cool in exposure.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, allowing any
OL,13,Fresidual cloud to dissipate and lead
OL,14,Fto a dry night with largely clear
OL,15,Fskies.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FGenerally fine and dry with
OL,18,Flight winds. Bright though staying
OL,19,Frather cloudy through the day. Feeling
OL,20,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
