OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fbut increasingly cloudy on Monday,
OL,7,Fsome possible rain late. Cloudier on
OL,8,FTuesday, with some rain at times.
OL,9,FBrighter and drier on Wednesday,
OL,10,Fthough becoming increasingly warm and
OL,11,Fhumid.
